===Noun===
'''su·per·no·va''' (''plural'' '''[[supernovae]]''' ''or'' '''[[supernovas]]''')

#[[Star]] which explodes, increasing its brightness to typically a billion times that of our [[sun]], though attenuated by the great distance from our sun.
#Those which leave only debris (Type I); others which fade to [[invisibility]] as [[neutron]] stars (Type II). 

